{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779202595561,"sessionID":"ses_1bf436535ffe3kjbOiU3XrlIGo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_04_E2tjikAJIczacokSkp9D8208","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/CONTRACT_VALIDATION.md"},"output":"<path>/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/status/CONTRACT_VALIDATION.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: phase: integrate-contract-validation\n2: dtos_checked: 2\n3: forms_checked: 11\n4: mismatches_found: 4\n5: \n6: ## Mismatches\n7: \n8: | DTO | Field | Backend Expects | Frontend Sends | Severity |\n9: |-----|-------|-----------------|----------------|----------|\n10: | LoginDto | password | min 8 chars (`PROJECT_API.md` — `/auth/login`) | min 6 chars (`frontend/app/utils/validations/auth.ts:5`) | HIGH |\n11: | CreatePropertyDto | address | flat fields: `addressStreet`, `addressCity`, `addressState`, `addressZipCode` (`backend/src/modules/properties/entities/property.entity.ts:48-58`) | nested object: `{street, city, state, zipCode}` (`frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts:4-11`, `frontend/app/pages/admin/property-form.tsx:28-33`) | MEDIUM |\n12: | PropertySearchParams | sortBy | `sortBy: string` + `sortOrder: 'ASC' \\| 'DESC'` (`backend/src/shared/dtos/pagination.dto.ts:28-36`) | combined: `'price_asc' \\| 'price_desc' \\| 'newest' \\| 'oldest'` (`frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts:70`) | MEDIUM |\n13: | InquiryFilters | sortBy | same `sortBy` + `sortOrder` pattern from `PaginationDto` | `'newest' \\| 'oldest'` (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:67`) | MEDIUM |\n14: \n15: ### Mismatch Details\n16: \n17: #### 1. Login password min length (HIGH)\n18: - **Backend contract** (`PROJECT_API.md`): password requires \"min 8 chars\"\n19: - **Frontend validation** (`frontend/app/utils/validations/auth.ts:4-5`):\n20:   ```ts\n21:   password: z.string().min(6, \"Password must be at least 6 characters\"),\n22:   ```\n23: - **Impact**: Users can submit passwords of length 6-7 characters that pass frontend validation but will be rejected by the backend with a 400 error.\n24: \n25: #### 2. Property address structure (MEDIUM)\n26: - **Backend entity** (`backend/src/modules/properties/entities/property.entity.ts:48-64`):\n27:   ```ts\n28:   @Column({ name: 'address_street', ... }) addressStreet: string;\n29:   @Column({ name: 'address_city', ... })  addressCity: string;\n30:   @Column({ name: 'address_state', ... }) addressState: string;\n31:   @Column({ name: 'address_zip_code', ... }) addressZipCode: string;\n32:   @Column({ name: 'address_latitude', ... }) addressLatitude: number | null;\n33:   @Column({ name: 'address_longitude', ... }) addressLongitude: number | null;\n34:   ```\n35: - **Frontend DTO** (`frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts:4-11`) and form (`frontend/app/pages/admin/property-form.tsx:28-33`):\n36:   ```ts\n37:   address: {\n38:     street: string;\n39:     city: string;\n40:     state: string;\n41:     zipCode: string;\n42:     latitude?: number;\n43:     longitude?: number;\n44:   }\n45:   ```\n46: - **Impact**: The frontend sends a nested `address` object, but the backend entity stores address fields as flat columns. A DTO transformer would be needed on the backend to map between these structures, or the frontend needs to flatten the address fields.\n47: \n48: #### 3. Property search sortBy convention (MEDIUM)\n49: - **Backend PaginationDto** (`backend/src/shared/dtos/pagination.dto.ts:28-36`):\n50:   ```ts\n51:   sortBy?: string;        // field name, e.g. 'createdAt'\n52:   sortOrder?: 'ASC' | 'DESC';  // direction\n53:   ```\n54: - **Frontend PropertySearchParams** (`frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts:70`):\n55:   ```ts\n56:   sortBy?: 'price_asc' | 'price_desc' | 'newest' | 'oldest';\n57:   ```\n58: - **Impact**: The frontend combines field and direction into a single string value (`price_asc`), while the backend expects them as two separate parameters. The frontend values won't be recognized by the backend's intended sort system.\n59: \n60: #### 4. Inquiry sortBy convention (MEDIUM)\n61: - **Same root cause as #3**: `InquiryFilters.sortBy` uses `'newest' | 'oldest'` (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:67`) instead of the backend's separate `sortBy` + `sortOrder` pattern from `PaginationDto`.\n62: - **Impact**: Same as mismatch #3 — different sort parameter conventions.\n63: \n64: ## Matched Contracts\n65: \n66: | DTO | Fields | Status |\n67: |-----|--------|--------|\n68: | LoginDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:1-4`) | `email`, `password` — field names and types match API contract; `login.tsx` sends `{email, password}` correctly | MATCH (except password min, listed above) |\n69: | RegisterDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:6-11`) | `name`, `email`, `password`, `phone?` — all fields match API contract `/auth/register` | MATCH |\n70: | ForgotPasswordDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:37-39`) | `email` — matches API contract `/auth/forgot-password` | MATCH |\n71: | ResetPasswordDto (`frontend/app/types/api/auth.d.ts:41-43`) | `token`, `password` — matches API contract `/auth/reset-password` | MATCH |\n72: | UpdateProfileDto (`frontend/app/types/api/profile.d.ts:13-15`) | `name?`, `phone?` — sent correctly from `profile.tsx:33-34` | MATCH |\n73: | SubmitInquiryDto (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:25-30`) | `message`, `name?`, `email?`, `phone?` — sent correctly from `detail.tsx:46-50` | MATCH |\n74: | RespondToInquiryDto (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:45-47`) | `response` — sent correctly from `inquiries.tsx:26` | MATCH |\n75: | UpdateUserStatusDto (`frontend/app/types/api/admin.d.ts:43-45`) | `status: 'active' \\| 'suspended'` — sent correctly from `users.tsx:18`; values match backend `UserStatusEnum` | MATCH |\n76: | AddFavoriteDto (`frontend/app/types/api/favorite.d.ts:25-27`) | `propertyId` — sent correctly from `search.tsx:97` and `detail.tsx:35` | MATCH |\n77: | PaginationDto (backend) | `page?`, `limit?`, `sortBy?`, `sortOrder?`, `search?` — no direct form, used as query params | N/A (no form, query pattern differs) |\n78: | RegisterDto → signup.tsx | `name` (mapped from `fullName`), `email`, `password`, `phone` — correct mapping at `signup.tsx:34-38` | MATCH |\n79: | RegisterDto → register.tsx | `name`, `email`, `password` (no `phone` field, but optional so acceptable) | MATCH |\n80: \n81: ## Audit Notes\n82: \n83: - **Backend DTOs are minimal**: Only `PaginationDto` and `ResponsePayloadDto` exist in the backend. There are no module-level Create*/Update* DTOs yet — only entity definitions. The backend is in early development with entities defined but no controllers, services, or feature DTOs wired.\n84: - **Frontend uses client-side type declarations** (`frontend/app/types/api/*.d.ts`) rather than sharing DTO definitions from the backend. These type files serve as the de facto contract.\n85: - **PaginationDto sort convention** is referenced by two different frontend filter types (`PropertySearchParams`, `InquiryFilters`), both using a different sorting pattern.\n86: - **Two registration forms exist** (`register.tsx` and `signup.tsx`), both calling the same `useRegister()` hook. `signup.tsx` includes the optional `phone` field; `register.tsx` does not. Both map to `RegisterDto` correctly.\n87: - **Dead code**: `utils/validations/auth.ts` exports `registerSchema` and `RegisterFormData` but no form uses them — both registration forms define their own inline schemas.\n88: - **Role and status enum values** between frontend (`'renter' | 'admin'`, `'active' | 'suspended'`) and backend (`RoleEnum.RENTER`, `RoleEnum.ADMIN`, `UserStatusEnum.ACTIVE`, `UserStatusEnum.SUSPENDED`) are aligned.\n89: - **PropertyType values** match: frontend `PROPERTY_TYPES = ['apartment', 'house', 'condo', 'townhouse', 'studio']` vs backend `PropertyTypeEnum`.\n90: - **InquiryStatus values** match: frontend `'new' | 'read' | 'responded'` vs backend `InquiryStatusEnum`.\n\n(End of file - total 90 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"phase: integrate-contract-validation\ndtos_checked: 2\nforms_checked: 11\nmismatches_found: 4\n\n## Mismatches\n\n| DTO | Field | Backend Expects | Frontend Sends | Severity |\n|-----|-------|-----------------|----------------|----------|\n| LoginDto | password | min 8 chars (`PROJECT_API.md` — `/auth/login`) | min 6 chars (`frontend/app/utils/validations/auth.ts:5`) | HIGH |\n| CreatePropertyDto | address | flat fields: `addressStreet`, `addressCity`, `addressState`, `addressZipCode` (`backend/src/modules/properties/entities/property.entity.ts:48-58`) | nested object: `{street, city, state, zipCode}` (`frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts:4-11`, `frontend/app/pages/admin/property-form.tsx:28-33`) | MEDIUM |\n| PropertySearchParams | sortBy | `sortBy: string` + `sortOrder: 'ASC' \\| 'DESC'` (`backend/src/shared/dtos/pagination.dto.ts:28-36`) | combined: `'price_asc' \\| 'price_desc' \\| 'newest' \\| 'oldest'` (`frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts:70`) | MEDIUM |\n| InquiryFilters | sortBy | same `sortBy` + `sortOrder` pattern from `PaginationDto` | `'newest' \\| 'oldest'` (`frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts:67`) | MEDIUM |\n\n### Mismatch Details\n\n#### 1. Login password min length (HIGH)\n- **Backend contract** (`PROJECT_API.md`): password requires \"min 8 chars\"\n- **Frontend validation** (`frontend/app/utils/validations/auth.ts:4-5`):\n  ```ts","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/status/CONTRACT_VALIDATION.md","time":{"start":1779202595263,"end":1779202595560}},"id":"prt_e40bd1378001nCJKNc3g9IFMM7","sessionID":"ses_1bf436535ffe3kjbOiU3XrlIGo","messageID":"msg_e40bce235001djFoBX4H90uOVC"}}
