{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1779203245042,"sessionID":"ses_1bf436535ffe3kjbOiU3XrlIGo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_00_izpTybp9T6IoTLrqPMLe3745","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/agent-logs/fix-receipt-fix-contracts-1.md","content":"fix_attempt: 1\nstatus: completed\ncontract_mismatches_fixed: 4\n\n## Fix Summary\n\nAll 4 contract mismatches resolved by fixing the frontend to match backend DTO contracts.\n\n### 1. Login password min length (HIGH)\n- **File**: `frontend/app/utils/validations/auth.ts`\n- **Change**: `min(6, ...)` → `min(8, ...)` for both `loginSchema` and `registerSchema`\n\n### 2. Property address structure (MEDIUM)\n- **Files changed**:\n  - `frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts` — removed `PropertyAddress` interface, flattened `PropertyListItem`, `PropertyDetail`, `CreatePropertyDto`, `UpdatePropertyDto`\n  - `frontend/app/types/api/favorite.d.ts` — flattened `FavoriteItem.property.address` to `addressCity`, `addressState`\n  - `frontend/app/pages/admin/property-form.tsx` — form fields and submit payload use flat address fields\n  - `frontend/app/pages/renter/search.tsx` — display uses `addressStreet`, `addressCity`, `addressState`\n  - `frontend/app/pages/renter/favorites.tsx` — display uses `addressCity`, `addressState`\n  - `frontend/app/pages/renter/detail.tsx` — display uses flat address fields (×2 locations)\n  - `frontend/app/pages/landing.tsx` — display uses flat address fields\n  - `frontend/app/pages/admin/properties.tsx` — display uses flat address fields\n\n### 3. PropertySearchParams sortBy (MEDIUM)\n- **File**: `frontend/app/types/api/property.d.ts`\n- **Change**: `sortBy?: 'price_asc' | ...'` → `sortBy?: string; sortOrder?: 'ASC' | 'DESC'`\n- **File**: `frontend/app/pages/renter/search.tsx`\n  - Added `SORT_OPTIONS` mapping UI values to `{sortBy, sortOrder}` pairs\n  - Updated initial state and filter update logic\n- **File**: `frontend/app/pages/landing.tsx` — `sortBy: 'createdAt', sortOrder: 'DESC'`\n- **File**: `frontend/app/pages/admin/properties.tsx` — `sortBy: 'createdAt', sortOrder: 'DESC'`\n\n### 4. InquiryFilters sortBy (MEDIUM)\n- **File**: `frontend/app/types/api/inquiry.d.ts` — `sortBy?: 'newest' | 'oldest'` → `sortBy?: string; sortOrder?: 'ASC' | 'DESC'`\n- **File**: `frontend/app/pages/admin/inquiries.tsx` — `sortBy: 'createdAt', sortOrder: 'DESC'`\n- **File**: `frontend/app/pages/renter/inquiries.tsx` — `sortBy: 'createdAt', sortOrder: 'DESC'`\n\n### Bonus\n- **File**: `frontend/app/types/api/admin.d.ts` — `UserFilters.sortBy` also fixed to `sortBy?: string; sortOrder?: 'ASC' | 'DESC'`\n- **File**: `frontend/app/pages/admin/users.tsx` — updated to `sortBy: 'createdAt', sortOrder: 'DESC'`\n\nAll TypeScript type checks pass with `npx tsc --noEmit`.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/saifulpotential/Potential/nestfind-sample/.claude-project/nestfind/agent-logs/fix-receipt-fix-contracts-1.md","exists":true,"truncated":false},"title":".claude-project/nestfind/agent-logs/fix-receipt-fix-contracts-1.md","time":{"start":1779203244748,"end":1779203245041}},"id":"prt_e40c6a10a001SgKoDrgb3WRaPV","sessionID":"ses_1bf436535ffe3kjbOiU3XrlIGo","messageID":"msg_e40c69481001lWpP9I0PIZ1gqc"}}
